---
description: wave-foundation conventions and validation gates
alwaysApply: true
---

Read **`AGENTS.md`** (and `CLAUDE.md`) for full guidance. Key rules:

- Validation gates run on every commit and PR (pre-commit + `.github/workflows/self-check.yml`):
  secret-scan, file-size, and `SKILL.md` frontmatter via `scripts/validate-skills.py`.
- `staging/` is un-vetted harvest — don't treat it as canonical; the foundation is `plugin/`,
  `rules/`, `frameworks/`, `design-system/`, `scripts/`.
- "Consumed, not copied": extract the cross-project, product-agnostic subset; genericize before it lands.
- No hardcoded user paths (`$HOME`/`~`), no secrets in tracked files, Supabase staging-first.
